{"slug": "reliquary", "root": "reliquary", "category": "item", "gloss": "a container for holy relics", "definition": "A reliquary is a container made to hold holy relics — the bones or belongings of a saint — often a jeweled and precious box or shrine. Its purpose is enshrinement, not use: where a *censer* burns and a *chalice* offers, the reliquary keeps and displays sacred remains, honoring the power thought to reside in them.", "history": "From Latin *reliquiae*, 'remains' (from *relinquere*, 'to leave behind') — the same root as *relic* and *relinquish*, a vessel for holy leftovers. Because the relics inside were held to carry the saint's power, the container grew correspondingly precious: Kieckhefer notes reliquaries set with gems to render honor to the saints thus enshrined, the power of stones linked with the power of the holy dead. Some were engineered so that oil poured in at the top ran out sanctified by proximity to the relic, and grimoires borrowed the image — carry the characters 'like a reliquary.'", "def_sources": [{"label": "Kieckhefer, Magic in the Middle Ages", "where": "Medieval magic (PDF)"}, {"label": "Page, Magic in the Cloister", "where": "Medieval magic (PDF)"}, {"label": "Etymonline, s.v. reliquary (Latin reliquiae)", "where": "Etymology reference"}], "commentary": null, "commentary_sources": [], "is_keyword": false, "etymology": {"lang": "Latin", "origin": "Latin reliquiae 'remains' (relinquere 'to leave behind')", "first": "1650s", "note": "A jewelled box for holy leftovers; the same root as 'relic' and 'relinquish'.", "hook": "A gold box for sacred leftovers."}, "essay": null, "sources": ["Etymonline (Douglas Harper)", "Wiktionary", "classical lexica (Lewis & Short, LSJ, Bosworth–Toller)", "Ted's historical-magic DBs (WitchcraftStudiesDB, AgrippaDOP, MedievalMagicDB)"], "stats": {"flavor_total": 2, "oracle_total": 1, "in_flavor_cards": 2, "in_oracle_cards": 1, "name_match_count": 7, "by_variant": {"reliquary": 3}, "first_year": 1999, "colors": {"W": 5, "C": 2, "G": 3, "B": 1}, "by_year": {"1999": 1, "2017": 1, "2022": 1, "2023": 1, "2024": 1, "2025": 1, "2026": 3}}, "cards": [{"id": "a149ac31-b792-4fbe-903a-788bbdfd5e97", "name": "Reliquary Monk", "set": "UDS", "set_name": "Urza's Destiny", "released": "1999-06-07", "type_line": "Creature — Human Monk Cleric", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["W"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/2/4/243e9386-2a7f-406a-9ed3-77d4bf1b50fd.jpg?1782720404", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/2/4/243e9386-2a7f-406a-9ed3-77d4bf1b50fd.jpg?1782720404", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/uds/14/reliquary-monk?utm_source=api", "local": "img/reliquary/a149ac31-b792-4fbe-903a-788bbdfd5e97.jpg"}, {"id": "393e5331-4456-4ba3-b410-bb630bb053db", "name": "Knight of the Reliquary", "set": "IMA", "set_name": "Iconic Masters", "released": "2017-11-17", "type_line": "Creature — Human Knight", "rarity": "rare", "colors": ["G", "W"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/2/0/205df311-a72d-40f1-b2ea-9b30274bc9bd.jpg?1782748392", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/2/0/205df311-a72d-40f1-b2ea-9b30274bc9bd.jpg?1782748392", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/ima/203/knight-of-the-reliquary?utm_source=api", "local": "img/reliquary/393e5331-4456-4ba3-b410-bb630bb053db.jpg"}, {"id": "2fb13687-0518-4ba0-a5ae-dd609464b026", "name": "Roadside Reliquary", "set": "NEO", "set_name": "Kamigawa: Neon Dynasty", "released": "2022-02-18", "type_line": "Land", "rarity": "uncommon", "colors": [], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/8/0/8002de90-93fb-48ea-a849-40fdad0aef5a.jpg?1782702159", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/8/0/8002de90-93fb-48ea-a849-40fdad0aef5a.jpg?1782702159", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/neo/272/roadside-reliquary?utm_source=api", "local": "img/reliquary/2fb13687-0518-4ba0-a5ae-dd609464b026.jpg"}, {"id": "dca7102e-c020-4fdc-9b59-f186e3e615a5", "name": "Dusk Rose Reliquary", "set": "LCI", "set_name": "The Lost Caverns of Ixalan", "released": "2023-11-17", "type_line": "Artifact", "rarity": "uncommon", "colors": ["W"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/a/5/a5f231ef-4167-4b0a-b54c-a098b2eb2f6f.jpg?1782694605", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/a/5/a5f231ef-4167-4b0a-b54c-a098b2eb2f6f.jpg?1782694605", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/lci/10/dusk-rose-reliquary?utm_source=api", "local": "img/reliquary/dca7102e-c020-4fdc-9b59-f186e3e615a5.jpg"}, {"id": "528039f3-e8e6-499d-add4-43cf2d731b65", "name": "Essence Reliquary", "set": "MH3", "set_name": "Modern Horizons 3", "released": "2024-06-14", "type_line": "Artifact", "rarity": "uncommon", "colors": ["W"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/e/6/e65f4ae3-6b21-4827-9851-8a53628e254f.jpg?1782691387", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/e/6/e65f4ae3-6b21-4827-9851-8a53628e254f.jpg?1782691387", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/mh3/24/essence-reliquary?utm_source=api", "local": "img/reliquary/528039f3-e8e6-499d-add4-43cf2d731b65.jpg"}, {"id": "c23e5b80-08d2-4e24-9908-fe2aa4f30f6f", "name": "Reliquary Tower", "set": "SOC", "set_name": "Secrets of Strixhaven Commander", "released": "2026-04-24", "type_line": "Land", "rarity": "uncommon", "colors": [], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/e/2/e2a27742-08c1-4153-af7f-25a7a98f585e.jpg?1782683076", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/e/2/e2a27742-08c1-4153-af7f-25a7a98f585e.jpg?1782683076", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/soc/398/reliquary-tower?utm_source=api", "local": "img/reliquary/c23e5b80-08d2-4e24-9908-fe2aa4f30f6f.jpg"}, {"id": "4507df69-6bf7-43d6-a609-c032b61835d5", "name": "Wight of the Reliquary", "set": "SOC", "set_name": "Secrets of Strixhaven Commander", "released": "2026-04-24", "type_line": "Creature — Zombie Knight", "rarity": "rare", "colors": ["B", "G"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/a/8/a8c6ee26-fa74-4859-9a94-89b476d218d2.jpg?1782683123", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/a/8/a8c6ee26-fa74-4859-9a94-89b476d218d2.jpg?1782683123", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/soc/338/wight-of-the-reliquary?utm_source=api", "local": "img/reliquary/4507df69-6bf7-43d6-a609-c032b61835d5.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Liminal Hold", "set": "ECL", "html": "A <mark>reliquary</mark> is needed to pass through the eclipse safely. Without it, two warring selves will calcify into one.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/5/a5a40c16-7a5c-4ad1-be53-6b1b1be2affe.jpg?1782684142"}, {"card": "Reliquary Tower", "set": "SOC", "html": "Once guarded by the Knights of the <mark>Reliquary</mark>, the tower stands now protected only by its own remoteness, its dusty treasures open to plunder by anyone.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/e/2/e2a27742-08c1-4153-af7f-25a7a98f585e.jpg?1782683076"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Dragonbroods' Relic", "set": "TDM", "html": "{3}{W}{U}{B}{R}{G}, Sacrifice this artifact: Create a 4/4 Dragon creature token named <mark>Reliquary</mark> Dragon that&#x27;s all colors. It has flying, lifelink, and &quot;When this token enters, it deals 3 damage to any target.&quot; Activate only as a sorcery."}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/5/a5a40c16-7a5c-4ad1-be53-6b1b1be2affe.jpg?1782684142", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/a/5/a5a40c16-7a5c-4ad1-be53-6b1b1be2affe.jpg?1782684142", "card": "Liminal Hold"}}